{"tid":1039063,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]響IFC大戰韓妹，為港增光#yup#","createTime":"2019-02-27T07:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T08:19:47.000Z","uid":23189,"like":99,"dislike":457,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"165070c561c853d6eec3199e0fe64b3371a21791","tid":1039063,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"今日去IFC間翡翠拉麵小籠包度食lunch<br />\n咁䌓忙時間食好多人要搭枱啦，隔離坐咗一對韓妹。<br />\n啲韓妹坐姿衰到呢，已經夠窄仲要蹺腳，唔係啲女仕果款，係「二郎腿」果款，仲要腳底係對住我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食嘅過程已經不斷睥下佢，但佢都唔自覺，一路係咁「寵寵寵寵」傾計。<br />\n咁食完喇，佢哋就化返妝，即係其實你搽返唇膏嗰啲我都覺得無咩嘢，最痴線係佢竟然拎支香水出嚟噴！ 我仲食緊架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到我食完條氣都chok住chok住，就去買arabica咖啡飲<br />\n點知冤家路窄，嗰兩條韓妹就排我後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁講一講arabica個收銀位係點，佢哋鐘意放兩個menu出嚟一大一細，大就係講豆，細就係嘢飲，而條龍就由右至左咁排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁到我點啦，嗌咗兩杯latte，咁cashier姐姐就話我夠印花可以換一杯，所以淨係需要俾一杯錢，響依個時候啲韓妹推上嚟睇個細menu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVnO6WT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVnO6WT.png&h=a9ace9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖展示，佢哋推到個menu阻住八達通位，搞到我拍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依一個moment，我要爆喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一手拎咗佢哋睇緊個細menu，將佢扔咗去拎嘢飲果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTxWwqB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTxWwqB.png&h=d06f69b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓妹呆咗 口up up 「哎喲嚇死我」<br />\n<br />\n我就以勝利者嘅身份拍八達通以一杯嘅價錢買咗兩杯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我正式宣布韓同蝗根本上無分別，唔使俾面佢哋依啲賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：啲相事後先影，所以韓妹無圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4f0312d5ed0ee32322d8749034ef7cf5938ff8","tid":1039063,"uid":33359,"like":156,"dislike":31,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"如果個韓妹係定延咁樣<br />\n腳底對住我塊臉都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96334f3ea8ecaaad0dd5d9bdfc5f903aac370f87","tid":1039063,"uid":122134,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"有無用廣東話屌7佢地先<br />\n無就真係垃圾"},{"pid":"0fcd50312641e4dda1505368227ed1dd9db56142","tid":1039063,"uid":23189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc4f0312d5ed0ee32322d8749034ef7cf5938ff8","tid":1039063,"uid":33359,"like":156,"dislike":31,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"如果個韓妹係定延咁樣<br />\n腳底對住我塊臉都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:12:32.000Z","msg":"依家跟咗韓妹老闆？"},{"pid":"608a701ca2bb5281829b1c3cf6fc2d9816a2fea6","tid":1039063,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"96334f3ea8ecaaad0dd5d9bdfc5f903aac370f87","tid":1039063,"uid":122134,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"有無用廣東話屌7佢地先<br />\n無就真係垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"佢哋已經嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0670814740b71d72ea307e2f9a3b4e3961f736","tid":1039063,"uid":181905,"like":155,"dislike":9,"score":146,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:13:39.000Z","msg":"韓國人同大陸人根本無分別 係班港女先咁撚鍾意吹奏韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc783ce1a99e1c9c249910d41de8fc6ec12e5efe","tid":1039063,"uid":53498,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"re